Send a known request / flow of requests that yieldds your bearer to ATOR
Highlight the AREA you wnat to extract in left pane, select "from selection" and add
Highlight the area you want to REPLACE in right pane and select "add regex", make sure that whatever string(s) are included around the "(.*)" statement are verbatim in the replacment field along with the Extraction token variable name (ours is BEARER) EG:
Regex = Bearer (.*)
Replacement= Bearer BEARER

